  keyTakeaway: `Stablecoin freezes are one of the fastest recovery tools available. Tether and Circle can lock funds in minutes to days when given clear evidence. Learn to build strong evidence packages quickly. Act before the funds move to mixers or are bridged away. This skill separates good investigators from great ones.`,

