      scenario: `You ask for the wallet address they sent funds to. You trace the first transfer to a collector wallet. That collector received funds from 47 other victims in the same 48-hour window with nearly identical amounts and timing. The collector then sent everything to a master wallet that routed to Tron USDT.`,
      outcome: `You map the full cluster and share the collector and master addresses with community groups and exchanges. Two exchanges freeze incoming funds linked to the master wallet. Your friend and several others get partial recovery. You document the pattern for future cases.`,
