          correct: 2,
          hint: `What does the professional standard say?`,
          explanation: `C is correct. 90%+ with responsible disclosure is the professional threshold. 100% is impossible without a court verdict. Below 90% means 10%+ chance of defaming an innocent person — too high.`,
