          correct: 1,
          hint: `What's the priority when funds are still moving?`,
          explanation: `B is correct. When funds are actively moving, getting exchanges to freeze comes first (privately). The 48-hour window can run simultaneously with exchange contact. Alerting the suspect before the exchange acts could allow fund escape.`,
